         FD helps. It really does. I always FD after casting a few dots on an uber mob. I may even do it two or three times for whatever it gains me. True, sometimes it does not help at all. I can successfuly FD and still get summoned.  But its saved me plenty of times.  King Tormax is a good one to FD on.  Cast a bunch of dots - do him plenty damage, and you still usually get away with FD, and live, even if the whole raid party wipes. Vindi too.</P><P>-Smartweed Jackson, 60 Warlock, Druzzil Ro<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
