         I have Feigned on AoW after doing tons of damage.. no mob gets to *see thru* Feign Death. Not yet anyway..</P><P>If Feign is successful, you are off the aggro list until you get back up. You are effectively -dead- to the mob.</P><P>When you get up, whether or not you have aggro depends on a number of things.  Learning how to lose aggro is one of the tricks of the trade, and varies greatly from zone to zone.</P><P>Vtyn</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
